DTK service is900

for:
  InterSense IS-900 Precision Motion Tracker for Virtual Environments


This works on the Virginia Tech CAVE to serve the is900 Virtual
Environments devices.

 IS-900 Tracked Tracker
 IS-900 Tracked Wand

This is a featureless service.
Edit config.h and is900.C to configure it.



files installed and where and description
-----------------------------------------


 is900.so   `dtk-config --server-dso-dir`

 A very simple featureless DTK service that serves two IS (Intersense
Inc.) devices using the IS900 control box.  The devices are (port 1)
"Tracked Tracker", head Tracker, and (port 2) "Tracked Wand", wand
with tracker.  This is used in the Virginia Tech CAVE at the time of
writing this.


 dtk-is900  `dtk-config --root`/bin

 A very small shell script used to start a DTK server with the above
service.

